def_cn: 辛迪加;私人联合会;企业联合组织
def_en: A syndicate is an association of people or organizations that is formed for business purposes or in order to carry out a project.

def_cn: 把(新闻或电视节目)同时出售给多家媒体(供其发表或播放)
def_en: When newspaper articles or television programmes are syndicated, they are sold to several different newspapers or television stations, who then publish the articles or broadcast the programmes.
A press syndicate is a group of newspapers or magazines that are all owned by the same person or company.
